\">CCC</a>, October 27, 2018</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sliding_Piece_Attacks&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73063\">New RookAttacks() - possibly</a> by <a href=\"/Michael_Sherwin\" title=\"Michael Sherwin\">Michael Sherwin</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 12, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73082\">scan-cut slider attack generation</a> by <a href=\"/Martin_Sedlak\" title=\"Martin Sedlak\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 13, 2020 &#160;» <a href=\"/Bitfoot#ABBitboards\" title=\"Bitfoot\">A/B Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73083\">Split Index Super Set Yielding (SISSY) Bitboards</a> by <a href=\"/Michael_Sherwin\" title=\"Michael Sherwin\">Michael Sherwin</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 13, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/SISSY_Bitboards\" title=\"SISSY Bitboards\">SISSY Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=77133\">I did some magic bitboard \"science\" and mostly learned not to worry about it</a> by  <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jakob_Progsch&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jakob Progsch (page does not exist)\">Jakob Progsch</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 20, 2021</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=78693\">Combining two of Bob's c